dc_title_s: Map showing land grants and railroad crossings along the Hackensack River, Bergen County, New Jersey
dc_description_s: Map showing the riparian grants and leases along the Hackensack River, Bergen County, New Jersey and the location of railroads and bridges in relation to the properties.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Date is inferred from most recent property lease.|Map is marked Bergen County No. 3
